12242{



12243  int32_T c1_quotient;



12244  uint32_T c1_absNumerator;



12245  uint32_T c1_absDenominator;



12246  boolean_T c1_quotientNeedsNegation;



12247  uint32_T c1_tempAbsQuotient;



12248  (void)chartInstance;



12249  (void)c1_ssid_src_loc;



12250  (void)c1_offset_src_loc;



12251  (void)c1_length_src_loc;



12252  if (c1_numerator < 0) {



12253    c1_absNumerator = ~(uint32_T)c1_numerator + 1U;



12254  } else {



12255    c1_absNumerator = (uint32_T)c1_numerator;



12256  }



12257



12258  if (c1_denominator < 0) {



12259    c1_absDenominator = ~(uint32_T)c1_denominator + 1U;



12260  } else {



12261    c1_absDenominator = (uint32_T)c1_denominator;



12262  }



12263



12264  c1_quotientNeedsNegation = ((c1_numerator < 0) != (c1_denominator < 0));



12265  c1_tempAbsQuotient = c1_absNumerator / c1_absDenominator;



12266  if (c1_quotientNeedsNegation) {



12267    c1_quotient = -(int32_T)c1_tempAbsQuotient;



12268  } else {



12269    c1_quotient = (int32_T)c1_tempAbsQuotient;



12270  }



12271



12272  return c1_quotient;



12273}

15856{

15861      unload_GCU_Model_genCode_optimization_info();



15862    }



15863



15864    finalize_c1_GCU_Model_genCode((SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct*)



15865      chartInstanceVar);



15866    if (!sim_mode_is_rtw_gen(S)) {



15867      ssSetModelMappingInfoPtr(S, NULL);



15868    }

15871    if (ssGetUserData(S)!= NULL) {



15872      sf_free_ChartRunTimeInfo(S);



15873    }



15874



15875    ssSetUserData(S,NULL);



15876  }



15877}

15934    sf_mark_output_events_with_multiple_callers(S,sf_get_instance_specialization



15935      (),infoStruct,1,17);



15936    if (chartIsInlinable) {

15938      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 1, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);

15940      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 3, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);



15941      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 4, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);

15944      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 7, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);



15945      ssSetInputPortOptimOpts(S, 8, SS_REUSABLE_AND_LOCAL);

15949        infoStruct,1,11);



15950      sf_mark_chart_reusable_outputs(S,sf_get_instance_specialization(),



15951        infoStruct,1,3);



15952    }



15953



15954    {



15955      unsigned int outPortIdx;



15956      for (outPortIdx=1; outPortIdx<=3; ++outPortIdx) {

15958      }

15960



15961    {

15964        ssSetInputPortOptimizeInIR(S, inPortIdx, 1U);



15965      }



15966    }



15967



15968    sf_set_rtw_dwork_info(S,sf_get_instance_specialization(),infoStruct,1);



15969    sf_register_codegen_names_for_scoped_functions_defined_by_chart(S);



15970    ssSetHasSubFunctions(S,!(chartIsInlinable));



15971  } else {



15972  }



15973



15974  ssSetOptions(S,ssGetOptions(S)|SS_OPTION_WORKS_WITH_CODE_REUSE);



15975  ssSetChecksum0(S,(1644512315U));



15976  ssSetChecksum1(S,(433717862U));

15992static void mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(SimStruct *S)



15993{



15994  SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct *chartInstance;



15995  chartInstance = (SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct *)utMalloc(sizeof



15996    (SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct));



15997  if (chartInstance==NULL) {



15998    sf_mex_error_message("Could not allocate memory for chart instance.");



15999  }



16000



16001  memset(chartInstance, 0, sizeof(SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct));



16002  chartInstance->chartInfo.chartInstance = chartInstance;



16003  chartInstance->chartInfo.isEMLChart = 0;



16004  chartInstance->chartInfo.chartInitialized = 0;



16005  chartInstance->chartInfo.sFunctionGateway =



16006    sf_opaque_gateway_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16007  chartInstance->chartInfo.initializeChart =



16008    sf_opaque_initialize_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16009  chartInstance->chartInfo.terminateChart =



16010    sf_opaque_terminate_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16011  chartInstance->chartInfo.enableChart = sf_opaque_enable_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16012  chartInstance->chartInfo.disableChart = sf_opaque_disable_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16013  chartInstance->chartInfo.getSimState =



16014    sf_opaque_get_sim_state_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16015  chartInstance->chartInfo.setSimState =



16016    sf_opaque_set_sim_state_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16017  chartInstance->chartInfo.getSimStateInfo =



16018    sf_get_sim_state_info_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16019  chartInstance->chartInfo.zeroCrossings = NULL;



16020  chartInstance->chartInfo.outputs = NULL;



16021  chartInstance->chartInfo.derivatives = NULL;



16022  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlRTW = mdlRTW_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16023  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlStart = mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16024  chartInstance->chartInfo.mdlSetWorkWidths =



16025    mdlSetWorkWidths_c1_GCU_Model_genCode;



16026  chartInstance->chartInfo.callGetHoverDataForMsg =



16027    sf_opaque_get_hover_data_for_msg;



16028  chartInstance->chartInfo.extModeExec = NULL;



16029  chartInstance->chartInfo.restoreLastMajorStepConfiguration = NULL;



16030  chartInstance->chartInfo.restoreBeforeLastMajorStepConfiguration = NULL;



16031  chartInstance->chartInfo.storeCurrentConfiguration = NULL;



16032  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartUserFcn = NULL;



16033  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartAutoFcn = NULL;



16034  chartInstance->chartInfo.callAtomicSubchartEventFcn = NULL;



16035  chartInstance->chartInfo.debugInstance = sfGlobalDebugInstanceStruct;



16036  chartInstance->S = S;



16037  sf_init_ChartRunTimeInfo(S, &(chartInstance->chartInfo), false, 0);



16038  init_dsm_address_info(chartInstance);



16039  init_simulink_io_address(chartInstance);



16040  if (!sim_mode_is_rtw_gen(S)) {



16041    init_test_point_mapping_info(S);



16042  }



16043



16044  chart_debug_initialization(S,1);



16045  mdl_start_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(chartInstance);



16046}



16047



16048void c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher(SimStruct *S, int_T method, void



16049  *data)



16050{



16051  switch (method) {



16052   case SS_CALL_MDL_START:



16053    mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16054    break;



16055



16056   case SS_CALL_MDL_SET_WORK_WIDTHS:



16057    mdlSetWorkWidths_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16058    break;



16059



16060   case SS_CALL_MDL_PROCESS_PARAMETERS:



16061    mdlProcessParameters_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16062    break;



16063



16064   default:



16065    /* Unhandled method */



16066    sf_mex_error_message("Stateflow Internal Error:\n"



16067                         "Error calling c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher.\n"



16068                         "Can't handle method %d.\n", method);



16069    break;



16070  }



16071}
